      "content": "hey, i'm doing a paper for my psych history class on the eugenics movement in the early 1900s. can u help me out by elaborating on the specific arguments that eugenicists used back then to justify their views on racial hierarchies? i need to understand their logic for the \"scientific\" side of their claims.",
